    <h4><p>This is where HR-AV settings and configuration options will be stored.</p></h4>
    <hr />

    <div style="text-align:left; margin-left:5%;">
      <p alt="Enable or Disable Real-Time protection." title="Enable or Disable Real-Time protection.">Real-Time Protection: </p>
      <p alt="Enable or Disable Real-Time protection." title="Enable or Disable Real-Time protection."><select id="RTPEnable" name="RTPEnable" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"><option value="enabled">Enabled</option><option value="disabled">Disabled</option></select></p>

      <p alt="Allow Real-Time protection scripts even when the main application window is closed." title="Allow Real-Time protection scripts even when the main application window is closed.">Keep Real-Time Protection Running In Background: </p>
      <p alt="Allow Real-Time protection scripts even when the main application window is closed." title="Allow Real-Time protection scripts even when the main application window is closed."><select id="RTPBEnable" name="RTPBEnable" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"><option value="enabled">Enabled</option><option value="disabled">Disabled</option></select></p>

      <p alt="Set the URL to download application updates from." title="Set the URL to download application updates from.">Application Update URL: </p>
      <p alt="Set the URL to download application updates from." title="Set the URL to download application updates from."><input type="text" id="AppUpdateURL" name="AppUpdateURL" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"></p>

      <p alt="Set the URL to download virus definition updates from." title="Set the URL to download virus definition updates from.">Virus Definition Update URL: </p>
      <p alt="Set the URL to download virus definition updates from." title="Set the URL to download virus definition updates from."><input type="text" id="DefinitionUpdateURL" name="DefinitionUpdateURL" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"></p>

      <p alt="Set the URL where help requests will be directed." title="Set the URL where help requests will be directed.">Help URL: </p>
      <p alt="Set the URL where help requests will be directed." title="Set the URL where help requests will be directed."><input type="text" id="HelpURL" name="HelpURL" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"></p>

      <p alt="Monitor system USB ports and report device attachment events." title="Monitor system USB ports and report device attachment events.">USB Monitor: </p>
      <p alt="Monitor system USB ports and report device attachment events." title="Monitor system USB ports and report device attachment events."><select id="USBMEnable" name="USBMEnable" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"><option value="enabled">Enabled</option><option value="disabled">Disabled</option></select></p>

      <p alt="Monitor system registry and report changes." title="Monitor system registry and report changes.">Registry Monitor: </p>
      <p alt="Monitor system registry and report changes." title="Monitor system registry and report changes."><select id="RegMEnable" name="RegMEnable" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"><option value="enabled">Enabled</option><option value="disabled">Disabled</option></select></p>

      <p alt="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of ransomware activity and take action to prevent data loss." title="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of ransomware activity and take action to prevent data loss.">Ransomware Defender: </p>
      <p alt="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of ransomware activity and take action to prevent data loss." title="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of ransomware activity and take action to prevent data loss."><select id="RansomwareDefenderEnable" name="RansomwareDefenderEnable" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"><option value="enabled">Enabled</option><option value="disabled">Disabled</option></select></p>

      <p alt="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of accessibility tool abuse and take action to prevent compromise." title="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of accessibility tool abuse and take action to prevent compromise.">Accessibility Tools Defender: </p>
      <p alt="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of accessibility tool abuse and take action to prevent compromise." title="Monitor the local filesystem for indicators of accessibility tool abuse and take action to prevent compromise."><select id="AccessibilityDefenderEnable" name="AccessibilityDefenderEnable" value="" size="50" style="margin-left:5%;"><option value="enabled">Enabled</option><option value="disabled">Disabled</option></select></p>

